# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. TOKEN & AUTH (Obrigatório para iniciar)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 1.1 Gerar Token de Cliente Akropoli
# Substitui o fluxo de connect-token da Pluggy
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/token
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

> {% client.global.set("akropoliAccessToken", response.body.access_token); %}


### 2.1 Listar Contas do Link
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/accounts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.2 Saldo de uma Conta Específica
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/accounts/{{accountId}}/balances
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.3 Limites da Conta
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/accounts/{{accountId}}/limits
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.4 Transações da Conta
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/accounts/{{accountId}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2.5 Transações Atuais (Recent)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/accounts/{{accountId}}/transactions-current
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 3. CREDIT CARDS (Cartões)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 3.1 Listar Cartões
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/credit-cards
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.2 Detalhes de um Cartão
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/credit-cards/{{cardId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.3 Limites do Cartão
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/credit-cards/{{cardId}}/limits
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.4 Faturas (Bills) do Cartão
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/credit-cards/{{cardId}}/bills
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.5 Transações da Fatura Específica
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/credit-cards/{{cardId}}/bills/{{billId}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3.6 Transações Gerais do Cartão
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/credit-cards/{{cardId}}/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 4. LOANS & FINANCINGS (Empréstimos e Financiamentos)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 4.1 Listar Empréstimos (Loans)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/loans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.2 Detalhes do Empréstimo
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/loans/{{contractId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.3 Garantias de Empréstimo
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/loans/{{contractId}}/warranties
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.4 Pagamentos de Empréstimo
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/loans/{{contractId}}/payments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.5 Parcelas Agendadas (Loans)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/loans/{{contractId}}/scheduled-instalments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4.6 Listar Financiamentos (Financings)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/financings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 5. INVESTMENTS (Fundos e Renda Fixa)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 5.1 Listar Fundos de Investimento
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/investments/funds
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5.2 Saldo em Fundos
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/investments/funds/{{investmentId}}/balances
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5.3 Renda Fixa Bancária
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/investments/bank-fixed-incomes
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 6. CUSTOMERS & RESOURCES (Dados Cadastrais)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### 6.1 Identificações do Cliente (Open Finance)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/identifications
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6.2 Recursos Disponíveis (Scope do Link)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/akropoli/links/{{itemId}}/data/resources
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}